---
---
<header class="py-8 px-4 max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
    <div class="text-center md:text-left">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-400 to-indigo-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            Rutina Semanal 🏋️
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mt-2">Gestiona tus entrenamientos diarios de forma eficiente.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center md:justify-end gap-3 w-full md:w-auto">
        <button 
            id="add-slot"
            class="bg-primary/10 text-primary border border-primary/20 px-6 py-3 sm:py-2 rounded-xl hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 font-medium active:scale-95 flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
        >
            <span class="text-xl">+</span> Agregar Rutina
        </button>
        <button 
            id="reset-all"
            class="bg-red-500/10 text-red-400 border border-red-500/20 px-6 py-3 sm:py-2 rounded-xl hover:bg-red-500 hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 font-medium active:scale-95 text-center"
        >
            Resetear Todo
        </button>
    </div>
</header>
